sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / SDK
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Webhook as Trainer Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Controller as TrainJob Controller<br/>(trainer-controller-manager)
    participant JobSetCtrl as JobSet Controller
    participant TrainingPod as Training Pods<br/>28080/TCP HTTP
    participant MPIWorker as MPI Worker Pods<br/>22/TCP SSH

    Note over User,MPIWorker: Flow 1: TrainJob Reconciliation

    User->>K8sAPI: POST TrainJob CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token/kubeconfig
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /validate-...-trainjob<br/>9443/TCP, TLS (self-signed)<br/>Auth: API server client cert
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validation Response
    K8sAPI-->>User: TrainJob Created

    K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch Event: TrainJob
    Controller->>K8sAPI: GET TrainingRuntime/ClusterTrainingRuntime<br/>443/TCP, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Runtime Spec

    Controller->>K8sAPI: CREATE JobSet<br/>443/TCP, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: CREATE NetworkPolicy<br/>443/TCP, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token

    K8sAPI->>JobSetCtrl: Watch Event: JobSet
    JobSetCtrl->>K8sAPI: CREATE Training Pods

    Note over User,MPIWorker: Flow 2: Progression Tracking (RHAI)

    Controller->>K8sAPI: LIST Pods (training job)<br/>443/TCP, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Pod IPs
    Controller->>TrainingPod: GET /metrics<br/>28080/TCP, HTTP, plaintext<br/>Auth: NetworkPolicy-restricted
    TrainingPod-->>Controller: Training Progress JSON
    Controller->>K8sAPI: PATCH TrainJob annotations<br/>443/TCP, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token

    Note over User,MPIWorker: Flow 3: MPI Training Setup

    Controller->>K8sAPI: CREATE SSH Secret<br/>(RSA key pair)
    Controller->>K8sAPI: CREATE hostfile ConfigMap
    Note over TrainingPod,MPIWorker: MPI Launcher → Worker communication
    TrainingPod->>MPIWorker: SSH connection<br/>22/TCP, SSH RSA keys

    Note over User,MPIWorker: Flow 4: PyTorch Distributed Training

    Note over TrainingPod: Node-0 ↔ Node-N<br/>29500/TCP (rendezvous)<br/>Dynamic/TCP (NCCL)<br/>plaintext, NetworkPolicy
